General.Name: Harris Technology Group Ltd
General.Description: Harris Technology Group Limited engages in the technology distribution and online retailing businesses in Australia. It is involved in the online retail of IT products and consumer electronics. The company sells its products through own eCommerce site ht.com.au, as well as online marketplace platforms, such as Amazon, eBay, Catch, and others. Harris Technology Group Limited was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Hallam, Australia.
